snippet.title: Darkest Dungeon II - The Binding Blade DLC Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
#darkestdungeon2 #darkestdungeon #redhook 

Darkest Dungeon II's first DLC pack, The Binding Blade, is launching on the Epic Games Store and Steam this December. 

Get 2 new heroes, a wandering miniboss and more. Wishlist now!
Steam: https://bit.ly/bindingbladesteam
Epic: https://bit.ly/bindingbladeepic

For more on Darkest Dungeon II:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1940340/Darkest_Dungeon_II/ 
Epic Game Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/darkest-dungeon-2 
Website: https://www.darkestdungeon.com
Discord: https://www.discord.gg/darkestdungeon/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DarkestDungeon
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DarkestDungeon
Instagram: https://instagram.com/redhookstudios
